<div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
  <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
    Upload a list of ingredients the National Poisons Information Service needs to know about
  </h1>
  <p class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-3">To tell us about the exact concentrations, you need to upload a PDF which lists the ingredients the National Poisons Information Service (NPIS) needs to know about in the product.</p>
  <p class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-3">List these ingredients in order of highest to lowest concentration.</p>
  <p class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">
  For every ingredient tell us the:
  </p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>International Nomenclature of Cosmetic Ingredients (INCI) name, where available</li>
    <li>exact concentrations (% w/w)</li>
  </ul>
</div>
